    strong_answer_analysis: 'Shows knowledge of Sridhar Vembu\'s philosophy, connects it to product decisions and pricing, makes a personal SE-relevant observation (not pushed to hit a number), and honestly acknowledges the trade-off (slower pace).',
    keywords: ['Sridhar Vembu', 'profitable', 'no VC pressure', 'Indian SMB focus', 'depth over speed', 'trade-off'],
