      steps: [
        { title: 'The Origin', description: 'Founded 2015, acquired by Flipkart, backed by Walmart. Started as a UPI payment app — competing with Google Pay, Paytm. Built dominance on UPI market share (consistently 40-50% of UPI transactions).' },
        { title: 'The Evolution', description: 'From payments app → financial super-app. Added: PhonePe Switch (mini-apps platform), Insurance, Mutual Funds (Wealth), Indus Appstore, and its Payment Gateway (for merchants). 2023: Separated from Flipkart, raised independently.' },
        { title: 'Current Revenue Model', description: 'UPI is zero-MDR (no direct transaction revenue). Revenue: Financial services (insurance commissions, mutual fund fees), Payment Gateway MDR for credit card transactions, advertising/partnerships within the app.' },
      ],
